    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Horde Survivor and Base Defense mashup</h2><br>Halftime Builders is a Horde Survival. Kill enemies in different ways depending your class, learn different blueprints as you level up, mount your defense and die. Buy upgrades from the shop and start again!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>5 different bosses<br></li><li>4 classes with different playstyles, be a mobile mech or mount your fortress<br></li><li>Compete with other players for the best highscore<br></li><li>Combine different buildings to balance the best offense/defense<br></li><li>Combines elements from Tower Defense, Horde Survivor and Roguelike games!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Different class with different playstyles!</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Build a stronghold</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342720/extras/b70db83561e9180c1656bad314004cb6.poster.avif?t=1737481012\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342720/extras/b70db83561e9180c1656bad314004cb6.webm?t=1737481012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342720/extras/b70db83561e9180c1656bad314004cb6.mp4?t=1737481012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Form your destruction convoy</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342720/extras/f5075fc9c268d8a5fb4f1633ac1c76da.poster.avif?t=1737481012\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342720/extras/f5075fc9c268d8a5fb4f1633ac1c76da.webm?t=1737481012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps